FBIS4-41041 "drsov120_h_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-120 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 Moldova Snegur Sets Up Commission for Relations With Romania Snegur Sets Up Commission for Relations With Romania AU2106184494 Bucharest Radio Romania Network in Romanian 1700 GMT 21 Jun 94 AU2106184494 Bucharest Radio Romania Network Romanian BFN [Cristian Nita dispatch from Chisinau] [Text] Today, in accordance with a decree by Mircea Snegur, the president of the Republic of Moldova, the Committee for Relations of the Republic of Moldova With Romania was set up, with the intention, quote, of ensuring efficient control over accords concluded by the Republic of Moldova and Romania in the field of economics, unquote. Mr. Ion Gutu, deputy prime minister of the Republic of Moldova, was appointed president of the committee.
